sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as Voyageur
    participant M as Mobile App
    participant API as NestJS API
    participant CS as ContentService
    participant WP as WordPressContentProvider
    participant WPR as WordPress REST API

    U->>M: Ouvre la liste des destinations
    M->>API: GET /content/destinations
    API->>CS: getDestinations()
    CS->>WP: getDestinations()
    WP->>WPR: Request custom content / posts
    WPR-->>WP: WordPress JSON response
    WP->>WP: Mapper les champs WordPress vers DestinationDto
    WP-->>CS: Liste normalisee des destinations
    CS-->>API: DestinationDto[]
    API-->>M: JSON normalise
    M-->>U: Afficher les destinations
